########
By Nytimz

Improves aim by:
1) Eliminating the annoying and overly-used fixed-shaped firing patterns on most guns (excluding Rocket Launchers).
2) Reducing arc of bullets (e.g. on the Hail or Tinderbox)
3) Speeding up bullets

Now it makes shotguns more reliable (shooting more bullets at aimpoint) while making guns like the Kitten deadly!
########

#Pistols#
set GD_Weap_Pistol.FiringModes.Bullets_Pistol_Bandit_Tinderbox Acceleration (X=0.000000,Y=0.000000,Z=-70.000000)
set GD_Weap_Pistol.FiringModes.Bullet_Pistol_Infinity FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Weap_Pistol.FiringModes.Bullets_Pistol_Torgue_Calla Speed 8000.000000

#Shotguns#
set GD_Weap_Shotgun.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_Blockhead FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Weap_Shotgun.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_ConferenceCall Speed 10000.000000
set GD_Weap_Shotgun.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_Heartbreaker FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Sage_Weapons.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_Hydra FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Sage_RaidWeapons.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_Interfacer Speed 10000.000000
set GD_Orchid_BossWeapons.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_JollyRoger FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Weap_Shotgun.FiringModes.Bullets_Shotgun_Torgue_Landscaper FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Weap_Shotgun.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_Octo FiringPatternLines ()
#    set GD_Aster_RaidWeapons.FiringModes.Bullets_Shotgun_Omen FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Aster_Weapons.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_Swordsplosion Speed 15000.000000
set GD_Weap_Shotgun.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_Teeth FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Weap_Shotgun.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_TidalWave FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Weap_Shotgun.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_Triquetra FiringPatternLines ()	
set GD_Sage_Weapons.FiringModes.Bullet_Shotgun_Twister FiringPatternLines ()	

#Assault Rifles#
set GD_Lobelia_Weapons.FiringModes.Bullet_Assault_Bekah Speed 15000.000000
set GD_Iris_Weapons.FiringModes.FM_Rocket_Grenade_BoomPuppy Speed 10000.000000
set GD_Weap_AssaultRifle.FiringModes.Bullet_Assault_Hail Acceleration (X=0.000000,Y=0.000000,Z=-1200.000000)
set GD_Iris_Weapons.FiringModes.Bullet_Assault_Kitten FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Sage_RaidWeapons.FiringModes.Bullet_Assault_Leadstorm Acceleration (X=0.000000,Y=0.000000,Z=-1200.000000)
set GD_Weap_AssaultRifle.FiringModes.Bullet_Assault_Bandit_Madhouse FiringPatternLines ()
set GD_Weap_AssaultRifle.FiringModes.Bullet_Assault_Dahl_Veruc FiringPatternLines ()

#Sniper Rifles#
set GD_Weap_SniperRifles.FiringModes.Bullet_Sniper_Longbow Speed 20000.000000
set GD_Weap_SniperRifles.FiringModes.Bullet_Sniper_Lyudmila Speed 20000.000000
set GD_Orchid_BossWeapons.FiringModes.Bullet_Sniper_Maliwan_Pimpernel Speed 20000.000000
